RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 1 7F Dirt CR: 36. Maiden Claiming Purse 6370. FOR MAIDENS, FILLIES AND MARES THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 120 lbs.; Older, 123 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Allowed 2 lbs. A Race Allowed 4 lbs. Claiming Price $8,000.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 3 1 1/8M Dirt CR: 87. Claiming Purse 8100. FOR FOUR YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD. Weight, 123 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since February 17 Allowed 2 lbs. A Race Since February 2 Allowed 4 lbs. A Race Since January 2 Allowed 7 lbs. Claiming Price $20,000.
